1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:03,545
Jangan berpikir sedetik pun

2
00:00:03,628 --> 00:00:06,005
bahwa aku sudah lupa tentang apa yang kamu lakukan pada saudaraku.

3
00:00:06,089 --> 00:00:09,217
Kakakmu meninggal karena kamu.

4
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:10,176
[Keduanya mendengus]

5
00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:11,219
TIDAK!

6
00:00:11,302 --> 00:00:14,180
[MENGERIKAN DAN BERTERIAK TERTINDAK]

7
00:00:15,015 --> 00:00:16,349
- Kejar mereka! - [WANITA] Liam!

8
00:00:16,433 --> 00:00:17,517
Cukup!

9
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,394
[Olsen dan Dado Mendengus]

10
00:00:20,603 --> 00:00:22,689
- [OLSEN MENGERUT] - [Es Merintih]

11
00:00:22,772 --> 00:00:24,566
Jangan sakiti dia lagi! Silakan!

12
00:00:26,401 --> 00:00:27,944
[LIAM] Jadi kamu masih hidup.

13
00:00:28,528 --> 00:00:29,571
[GWEN] Kamu sudah mati.

14
00:00:34,743 --> 00:00:37,412
- Tidak ada tempat untuk bersembunyi di sini. - [LUNA] Langit-langitnya.

15
00:00:37,495 --> 00:00:38,621
Buru-buru.

16
00:00:39,205 --> 00:00:41,833
Kita kehabisan waktu. Bergerak lebih cepat.

17
00:00:41,916 --> 00:00:44,127
- [RENCIAN KERAS] - Ssst!

18
00:00:45,962 --> 00:00:48,339
[HOMER] Apakah kamu pernah mencintaiku, Wendy?

19
00:00:48,423 --> 00:00:49,799
[WENDY] Aku sudah mencobanya.

20
00:00:49,883 --> 00:00:51,551
aku mencintaimu.

21
00:00:51,634 --> 00:00:53,595
Anda mengacaukan saya. Sama seperti Magnus!

22
00:00:53,678 --> 00:00:55,472
Mungkin kalian berdua bekerja sama.

23
00:00:55,555 --> 00:00:58,183
Mungkin Anda memberi tahu polisi, dan itulah sebabnya saya tertangkap.

24
00:00:58,266 --> 00:00:59,684
Saya tidak tahu apa yang Anda bicarakan!

25
00:00:59,768 --> 00:01:00,935
- Wendy-- - Dasar bajingan!

26
00:01:01,019 --> 00:01:02,520
[Keduanya mengerang]

27
00:01:02,604 --> 00:01:04,064
- [LUCAS] Pukul dia! - [WENDY] Hentikan!

28
00:01:04,564 --> 00:01:06,191
[SENJATA CEPAT]

29
00:01:07,317 --> 00:01:09,235
Anda belum bisa membunuhnya.

30
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,653
Kami masih membutuhkannya.

31
00:01:11,738 --> 00:01:13,114
[Keduanya mendengus]

32
00:01:14,157 --> 00:01:15,617
- pada? -Liam?

33
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:19,412
- [SENANG] Tuan Liam. - Nona Bahagia. Sukacita!

34
00:01:20,622 --> 00:01:21,498
Bos Emil!

35
00:01:21,581 --> 00:01:23,208
Kami punya masalah.

36
00:01:24,542 --> 00:01:26,085
[EMIL] Liam Roja.

37
00:01:26,169 --> 00:01:29,506
Jika Anda tidak kembali ke sini dalam lima menit,

38
00:01:30,673 --> 00:01:32,550
kamu tahu apa yang akan terjadi pada ibumu.

39
00:01:45,355 --> 00:01:46,523
[Atas] liam.

40
00:01:49,609 --> 00:01:55,949
[MEMUTAR MUSIK MENGAduk]

41
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:04,791
Kami sedang memasak.

42
00:02:06,835 --> 00:02:10,338
Kami membuat hidangan menggunakan bahan apa pun yang ada di sini.

43
00:02:10,421 --> 00:02:12,966
Yang tercepat, terlezat,

44
00:02:13,049 --> 00:02:14,717
dan cukup untuk banyak orang.

45
00:02:14,801 --> 00:02:16,052
Tuan Liam!

46
00:02:16,136 --> 00:02:18,763
Kita akan memasak di tengah semua bahaya ini?

47
00:02:18,847 --> 00:02:20,515
Inilah yang akan menyelamatkan kita.

48
00:02:20,598 --> 00:02:23,393
[MUSIK MENGAduk BERLANJUT]

49
00:02:23,476 --> 00:02:25,019
Dokter.

50
00:02:25,103 --> 00:02:27,605
Saya ingin Anda mendapatkan bahan yang paling penting.

51
00:02:28,606 --> 00:02:32,819
[MUSIK MENGAduk BERLANJUT]

52
00:02:33,570 --> 00:02:34,696
Saya akan kembali.

53
00:02:34,779 --> 00:02:36,197
- Luna? - Bung.

54
00:02:37,448 --> 00:02:40,201
Mereka perlu tertarik pada aroma masakan Anda.

55
00:02:40,827 --> 00:02:41,828
Kamu bisa.

56
00:02:43,121 --> 00:02:44,497
Hati-hati.

57
00:02:45,874 --> 00:02:47,041
Kamu juga.

58
00:02:50,003 --> 00:02:51,045
Pergi--

59
00:02:59,888 --> 00:03:06,853
{\an8}[PEMUTARAN MUSIK TEMA]

60
00:03:40,929 --> 00:03:42,847
{\an8}[MINNIE BATUK]

61
00:03:49,145 --> 00:03:50,355
{\an8}Yang Mulia.

62
00:03:51,522 --> 00:03:52,815
{\an8}Terima kasih.

63
00:03:54,984 --> 00:03:56,486
{\an8}- Ayah. - Mm?

64
00:03:56,569 --> 00:03:58,821
{\an8}Mama sakit lagi.

65
00:03:58,905 --> 00:04:00,281
{\an8}[GULPS]

66
00:04:00,365 --> 00:04:01,699
{\an8}Tidak, sayang.

67
00:04:02,742 --> 00:04:04,661
{\an8}Ibu bisa mengatasinya.

68
00:04:05,703 --> 00:04:07,872
{\an8}Ingat janjiku padamu?

69
00:04:07,956 --> 00:04:10,208
{\an8}Bahwa kita akan kembali ke rumah?

70
00:04:10,291 --> 00:04:11,501
{\an8}Ya.

71
00:04:12,794 --> 00:04:13,836
{\an8}Ya.

72
00:04:15,797 --> 00:04:21,636
{\an8}[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG MENGAduk]

73
00:04:38,152 --> 00:04:40,947
{\an8}[Terengah-engah]

74
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,742
{\an8}Sepertinya masih dalam.

75
00:04:48,621 --> 00:04:51,541
{\an8}Insinyur, seberapa jauh kita dari target kita?

76
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:53,960
{\an8}Tunggu, saya akan memeriksanya.

77
00:04:55,420 --> 00:05:01,926
{\an8}[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG MENGGANGGU]

78
00:05:17,066 --> 00:05:19,485
{\an8}Kira-kira tersisa tiga meter.

79
00:05:19,569 --> 00:05:22,864
{\an8}Kita akan mencapai pipa pembuangan limbah lama.

80
00:05:24,532 --> 00:05:26,451
{\an8}Setelah kamu berhasil melewatinya,

81
00:05:26,534 --> 00:05:29,454
{\an8}Anda akan memiliki jalan keluar dari rumah sakit ini.

82
00:05:29,537 --> 00:05:35,960
{\an8}[MUSIK YANG MENGGANGGU BERLANJUT]

83
00:05:36,711 --> 00:05:38,671
{\an8}Tekstur tanah berubah.

84
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:42,592
{\an8}Kalau sudah liat dan lunak seperti ini, kamu tidak bisa menggunakan bahan peledak lagi.

85
00:05:42,675 --> 00:05:44,802
{\an8}Terowongan bisa runtuh.

86
00:05:46,929 --> 00:05:51,726
{\an8}[MUSIK YANG MENGGANGGU BERLANJUT]

87
00:05:59,525 --> 00:06:04,405
[MEMUTAR MUSIK MENGAduk]

88
00:06:24,884 --> 00:06:31,140
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

89
00:06:40,108 --> 00:06:41,484
Masuklah, cepat!

90
00:06:42,026 --> 00:06:43,820
Kamu bergerak terlalu lambat.

91
00:06:43,903 --> 00:06:48,491
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

92
00:06:48,574 --> 00:06:49,617
A.

93
00:06:50,743 --> 00:06:52,870
Mereka mencoba mempermainkan kami.

94
00:06:53,788 --> 00:06:54,747
Berlututlah!

95
00:06:54,831 --> 00:06:56,791
- Nak! - [OLSEN MENDENGAR]

96
00:06:56,874 --> 00:06:58,334
Olsen!

97
00:06:58,417 --> 00:07:02,296
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

98
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:04,006
Mereka berhasil menyelinap membawa senjata.

99
00:07:05,091 --> 00:07:06,634
Mereka pintar.

100
00:07:16,144 --> 00:07:17,228
Dia anakmu?

101
00:07:17,311 --> 00:07:23,901
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

102
00:07:42,545 --> 00:07:45,173
Hanya saja, jangan bergerak terlalu jauh. Ini tidak akan meledak.

103
00:07:52,221 --> 00:07:53,347
- Tiga. - Apa?

104
00:07:53,431 --> 00:07:54,599
Kita kehabisan bom.

105
00:07:54,682 --> 00:07:56,142
Bagaimana dengan yang ini?

106
00:07:56,225 --> 00:07:57,226
Itu cukup.

107
00:07:58,603 --> 00:07:59,937
Jika dia mencoba melawan lagi,

108
00:08:01,189 --> 00:08:03,357
ibunya meledak.

109
00:08:04,025 --> 00:08:09,071
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

110
00:08:09,155 --> 00:08:10,239
[LANGKAH CEPAT]

111
00:08:10,323 --> 00:08:12,074
- [MAN 1] Apa itu?! - [MAN 2] Jatuhkan!

112
00:08:12,158 --> 00:08:13,201
Liam?

113
00:08:13,284 --> 00:08:14,160
[GRETA] Nak!

114
00:08:14,243 --> 00:08:15,411
Liam.

115
00:08:18,414 --> 00:08:19,415
Bergerak.

116
00:08:19,499 --> 00:08:21,751
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

117
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:23,544
Berjalan!

118
00:08:27,757 --> 00:08:28,841
- [THWACKS] - [TERIAK GRETA]

119
00:08:28,925 --> 00:08:30,551
- [LIAM mendengus] - [GRETA merengek]

120
00:08:30,635 --> 00:08:32,803
Putra! [MERINTAI]

121
00:08:32,887 --> 00:08:39,644
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

122
00:08:46,776 --> 00:08:50,196
Chef Luna, apa yang kita masak?

123
00:08:53,533 --> 00:08:54,659
Teman-teman.

124
00:08:54,742 --> 00:08:56,118
[mendesis]

125
00:08:58,538 --> 00:09:02,250
Kita membutuhkan hidangan yang menggugah selera hanya dari aromanya.

126
00:09:03,334 --> 00:09:04,794
Ada pemikiran?

127
00:09:04,877 --> 00:09:09,131
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK PENSIF]

128
00:09:09,215 --> 00:09:10,258
Eh…

129
00:09:16,097 --> 00:09:17,306
[Hembuskan napas dalam-dalam]

130
00:09:19,684 --> 00:09:20,893
[Terkesiap]

131
00:09:22,019 --> 00:09:23,604
Jamur ayam bawang putih.

132
00:09:23,688 --> 00:09:25,773
[EXHALES] Yang ala restoran?

133
00:09:25,856 --> 00:09:27,358
Ya.

134
00:09:27,441 --> 00:09:28,943
Gaya Chef Liam.

135
00:09:29,026 --> 00:09:31,696
Hanya aromanya saja, dan mereka tidak akan punya peluang.

136
00:09:31,779 --> 00:09:34,156
Tumis dengan api besar, banyak bawang putihnya.

137
00:09:34,782 --> 00:09:37,702
Joy, cincang banyak bawang putih dan banyak bawang bombay.

138
00:09:37,785 --> 00:09:41,038
Dan Anda, potong paprika, brokoli, kentang, dan jamur.

139
00:09:41,122 --> 00:09:43,708
- Ya, Koki. - Teman-teman, ini akan cepat.

140
00:09:43,791 --> 00:09:45,459
- Kami punya ini. - Ya, Koki.

141
00:09:45,543 --> 00:09:47,128
- Ya, Koki. - Oke.

142
00:09:47,211 --> 00:09:50,548
[MEMUTAR MUSIK MENGAduk]

143
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:54,719
Dimana temanmu?

144
00:09:54,802 --> 00:10:00,308
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

145
00:10:01,517 --> 00:10:02,727
- [GRETA WHIMPERS] - [MAGNUS] Tunggu--

146
00:10:02,810 --> 00:10:05,062
- [LIAM mendengus] - Hei! Tunggu! Hai!

147
00:10:05,146 --> 00:10:07,648
- [MAGNUS] Liam! - [GRETA merengek]

148
00:10:08,274 --> 00:10:09,525
[MEMOTONGAN]

149
00:10:09,609 --> 00:10:13,154
- Chef, harusnya seperti ini, atau lebih besar? - Oke.

150
00:10:13,237 --> 00:10:14,989
Seperti ini, Koki?

151
00:10:15,072 --> 00:10:16,240
Itu ukurannya.

152
00:10:16,324 --> 00:10:21,662
[MEMUTAR MUSIK MENGAduk]

153
00:10:22,246 --> 00:10:23,456
- Kamu mengerti? - Salin, Koki.

154
00:10:23,539 --> 00:10:24,749
Saya akan melakukan itu.

155
00:10:25,416 --> 00:10:27,877
- [DADO MENGERUT] - [GRETA MERINGIKAN]

156
00:10:28,628 --> 00:10:30,755
- [buang napas dengan tajam] - [LIAM BATUK]

157
00:10:30,838 --> 00:10:33,090
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

158
00:10:35,259 --> 00:10:37,053
Koki, haruskah saya menambahkan lebih banyak?

159
00:10:37,762 --> 00:10:39,889
- Apakah ini cukup? - eh…

160
00:10:39,972 --> 00:10:41,682
- Itu yang terakhir. - Oke.

161
00:10:41,766 --> 00:10:44,852
- Jadi, setelah itu, brokoli. - Baiklah.

162
00:10:45,353 --> 00:10:46,520
Kamu pikir kamu tangguh, ya?!

163
00:10:47,021 --> 00:10:48,064
- [GERAN] - [GRETA] Cukup!

164
00:10:48,147 --> 00:10:49,607
- Kamu pikir kamu tangguh, ya?! - [Mendengus]

165
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:50,941
- [GRETA MENGERIKAN] - [MENGERUT]

166
00:10:51,025 --> 00:10:54,362
[LIAM TERSEMBUNYI]

167
00:10:55,237 --> 00:11:00,910
[MEMUTAR MUSIK MENGAduk]

168
00:11:03,537 --> 00:11:05,498
Sekarang, kamu jinak.

169
00:11:05,581 --> 00:11:06,666
[BATUK]

170
00:11:08,417 --> 00:11:10,419
Aku akan bertanya padamu untuk terakhir kalinya.

171
00:11:10,503 --> 00:11:11,671
[CELANA]

172
00:11:11,754 --> 00:11:13,631
Dimana temanmu?

173
00:11:14,757 --> 00:11:20,846
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

174
00:11:26,602 --> 00:11:28,646
[MEMOTONGAN]

175
00:11:32,316 --> 00:11:34,068
Mereka bersembunyi di komisaris.

176
00:11:35,111 --> 00:11:37,696
[LIAM BERNAPAS BERAT, MENENGAH]

177
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,323
- Apakah kamu berbohong? - [Mendengus]

178
00:11:40,366 --> 00:11:41,325
Hah?!

179
00:11:44,036 --> 00:11:45,162
Bagaimana menurut Anda, bos?

180
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,917
- Coba lihat. - Ya, tuan!

181
00:11:53,003 --> 00:11:54,213
Berdiri!

182
00:11:55,756 --> 00:11:56,715
Berdiri!

183
00:11:57,466 --> 00:11:59,343
[Mendengus]

184
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:06,100
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

185
00:12:06,183 --> 00:12:08,644
Jika anakmu membodohiku,

186
00:12:09,395 --> 00:12:11,397
dia akan kembali kepadamu sebagai mayat.

187
00:12:13,858 --> 00:12:15,818
- Liam, kumohon... - Silakan!

188
00:12:16,569 --> 00:12:18,154
- Berjalanlah sekarang! - Buru-buru!

189
00:12:19,989 --> 00:12:21,615
- Buru-buru! - Hebat!

190
00:12:21,699 --> 00:12:27,872
[MUSIK TENSE BERLANJUT]

191
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:33,461
[MEMUTAR MUSIK MENGAduk]

192
00:12:33,544 --> 00:12:34,670
[PLATE CLINK]

193
00:12:36,589 --> 00:12:37,756
[MENDESIS]

194
00:12:39,967 --> 00:12:41,385
Ini bedaknya.

195
00:12:44,638 --> 00:12:45,931
Haruskah kita menambahkan ini, Chef?

196
00:12:46,015 --> 00:12:52,855
[MUSIK MENGAduk BERLANJUT]

197
00:12:57,776 --> 00:12:58,819
Tambahkan semua itu.

198
00:12:58,903 --> 00:13:01,113
[DENTING]

199
00:13:06,994 --> 00:13:08,454
Tunggu dulu, Bu Happy.

200
00:13:08,537 --> 00:13:09,538
- [goresan] - [terkekeh]

201
00:13:09,622 --> 00:13:14,835
[MUSIK MENGAduk BERLANJUT]

202
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:16,879
- Ayo, cicipi. - Baiklah.

203
00:13:16,962 --> 00:13:18,047
- Di Sini. - Hmm.

204
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:21,091
Koki, ini.

205
00:13:25,763 --> 00:13:27,723
- Baunya enak. - Hmm.

206
00:13:27,806 --> 00:13:29,850
- Sudah lama sekali sejak aku-- - [PINTU TERBUKA]

207
00:13:31,810 --> 00:13:33,187
Dokter! Hmm.

208
00:13:35,105 --> 00:13:36,106
Saya mengerti.

209
00:13:36,899 --> 00:13:38,025
Oke.

210
00:13:39,443 --> 00:13:40,444
Hmm.

211
00:13:41,987 --> 00:13:43,364
Hmm?

212
00:13:46,283 --> 00:13:47,493
Uh--

213
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,207
[TERKECIL SEDIKIT]

214
00:13:53,958 --> 00:13:55,125
Itu bagus.

215
00:13:55,209 --> 00:13:57,002
B-Benarkah?

216
00:14:00,422 --> 00:14:02,174
Itu adalah spesialisasi ibuku.

217
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,135
Itu makanan terakhir yang dia masak untuk kita

218
00:14:06,804 --> 00:14:08,973
sebelum dia meninggal karena leukemia.

219
00:14:10,391 --> 00:14:12,351
Dialah alasanku menjadi seorang dokter.

220
00:14:13,602 --> 00:14:15,354
Um... Maaf, Dok.

221
00:14:15,437 --> 00:14:16,814
Saya tidak tahu.

222
00:14:16,897 --> 00:14:20,192
Eh, aku yakin…

223
00:14:20,276 --> 00:14:22,403
ibumu akan sangat bangga padamu.

224
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:24,697
Terima kasih.

225
00:14:27,741 --> 00:14:29,076
[Terkekeh pelan]

226
00:14:30,077 --> 00:14:31,328
Jadi? Ayo kita lakukan?

227
00:14:31,412 --> 00:14:35,165
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG MENAKJUBKAN]

228
00:14:35,249 --> 00:14:37,001
Saya harap ini berhasil.

229
00:14:50,973 --> 00:14:57,521
[Musik yang menegangkan terus berlanjut]

230
00:15:01,442 --> 00:15:02,902
Koki, aduk.

231
00:15:09,867 --> 00:15:11,827
Awasi mereka.

232
00:15:18,292 --> 00:15:20,669
- Aku serahkan padamu. - Ya, bos.

233
00:15:24,632 --> 00:15:31,263
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TIDAK MUDAH]

234
00:15:31,347 --> 00:15:33,933
[Sengatan MUSIK GELAP]

235
00:15:35,392 --> 00:15:36,477
Apakah kamu hamil, Wendy?

236
00:15:37,061 --> 00:15:39,188
Oh, bukan aku.

237
00:15:40,439 --> 00:15:41,649
Alarm palsu.

238
00:15:41,732 --> 00:15:43,525
aku mencintaimu.

239
00:15:44,568 --> 00:15:46,654
Aku bermimpi mempunyai anak bersamamu.

240
00:15:46,737 --> 00:15:48,614
Tapi apa yang kamu lakukan?

241
00:15:49,281 --> 00:15:51,575
Saya senang kami tidak punya anak.

242
00:15:52,785 --> 00:15:57,164
Aku akan merasa kasihan pada anak itu, jika mempunyai ayah sepertimu.

243
00:16:05,589 --> 00:16:07,049
Apakah kamu baik-baik saja?

244
00:16:07,132 --> 00:16:13,263
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK PENSIF]

245
00:16:13,347 --> 00:16:14,640
Ketika kita…

246
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:18,560
Ketika kami berada di rumah staf…

247
00:16:20,938 --> 00:16:23,273
Guci Papa pecah.

248
00:16:25,859 --> 00:16:28,112
Mengapa diisi pasir?

249
00:16:30,864 --> 00:16:32,282
Aku tidak tahu.

250
00:16:33,659 --> 00:16:35,077
Kamu tidak?

251
00:16:38,914 --> 00:16:40,082
Anda tidak tahu.

252
00:16:45,295 --> 00:16:46,672
Aku mengenalmu, Bu.

253
00:16:47,881 --> 00:16:50,843
Saya tahu ketika Anda tidak mengatakan yang sebenarnya.

254
00:16:54,596 --> 00:16:57,474
Anda tidak memberi tahu saya apa yang terjadi antara Anda dan Sir Magnus.

255
00:16:59,601 --> 00:17:01,437
Apakah kamu akan merahasiakan ini dariku juga?

256
00:17:03,939 --> 00:17:06,066
Tidak masalah, Nak.

257
00:17:06,608 --> 00:17:10,404
Yang perlu Anda ketahui adalah bahwa dia adalah pria yang tidak berguna.

258
00:17:11,947 --> 00:17:15,284
Ayahku… belum mati?

259
00:17:18,037 --> 00:17:20,706
Apakah dia benar-benar mati atau masih hidup?

260
00:17:20,789 --> 00:17:26,086
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK SULLEN]

261
00:17:26,170 --> 00:17:27,796
Dia masih hidup?

262
00:17:31,008 --> 00:17:32,301
Bu.

263
00:17:39,516 --> 00:17:42,227
Anda membuat saya bertindak seperti orang bodoh sepanjang hidup saya?

264
00:17:45,856 --> 00:17:51,028
Kamu membuatku percaya bahwa aku tidak punya ayah. Bahwa dia telah meninggal.

265
00:17:53,155 --> 00:17:54,615
Setiap hari, setiap malam,

266
00:17:55,491 --> 00:17:57,785
sebelum tidur, setelah bangun tidur,

267
00:17:57,868 --> 00:18:00,621
Saya berdoa pada pasir.

268
00:18:00,704 --> 00:18:04,583
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK EMOSIONAL]

269
00:18:04,666 --> 00:18:06,168
Olsen, aku minta maaf.

270
00:18:06,251 --> 00:18:09,463
Aku tidak butuh permintaan maaf, Bu. Saya tidak membutuhkannya.

271
00:18:12,424 --> 00:18:13,675
Katakan yang sebenarnya.

272
00:18:15,010 --> 00:18:17,471
Katakan yang sebenarnya. Hanya itu yang saya minta.

273
00:18:18,847 --> 00:18:20,891
Kamu menyembunyikan banyak hal dariku.

274
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:26,396
Nama yang kamu katakan padaku,

275
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,857
apakah itu benar namanya?

276
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:33,195
Apakah dia masih hidup? Siapa ayah kandungku?

277
00:18:34,738 --> 00:18:35,739
Dengan baik?

278
00:18:38,283 --> 00:18:41,286
Siapa ayahku? Katakan yang sebenarnya.

279
00:18:43,622 --> 00:18:45,582
Kenapa kamu tidak memberitahunya?

280
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:52,214
[MUSIK SOMBER BERLANJUT]

281
00:19:04,226 --> 00:19:07,146
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG TENANG]

282
00:19:07,229 --> 00:19:08,480
[DADO] Cepatlah.

283
00:19:10,149 --> 00:19:14,695
Tarik cepat ke arahku lagi dan aku sendiri yang akan menembakmu.

284
00:19:16,405 --> 00:19:17,281
Pergi!

285
00:19:20,742 --> 00:19:27,624
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK YANG MENAKJUBKAN]

286
00:19:32,171 --> 00:19:35,007
{\an8}Jika kamu bertanya-tanya siapa ayahmu,

287
00:19:35,090 --> 00:19:39,469
{\an8}Aku juga penasaran apakah kamu anakku.

288
00:19:40,095 --> 00:19:42,222
{\an8}Kalian semua, berbarislah sekarang!

289
00:19:42,306 --> 00:19:43,307
{\an8}Bos, ini kelihatannya bagus.

290
00:19:44,391 --> 00:19:45,976
{\an8}Ambilkan kami piring! Buru-buru!

291
00:19:47,019 --> 00:19:49,688
{\an8}[HOMER] Jika aku kalah, aku akan melepaskan ibumu.

292
00:19:49,771 --> 00:19:53,400
{\an8}Jika aku mengalahkanmu, aku akan mendorong ibumu keluar gedung!

293
00:19:53,483 --> 00:19:57,654
{\an8}[MENGERUT]

294
00:19:57,738 --> 00:20:00,866
{\an8}[LAKI-LAKI MENGECEWAKAN]

295
00:20:01,533 --> 00:20:02,826
{\an8}[BATUK]

296
00:20:02,910 --> 00:20:06,288
{\an8}[MENGERUT]

297
00:20:06,371 --> 00:20:08,040
{\an8}[LIAM] Dia akan membunuh kita begitu mereka bangun!

298
00:20:09,166 --> 00:20:10,000
{\an8}[TEMBAKAN]

299
00:20:10,083 --> 00:20:12,878
{\an8}Jika seseorang melakukan kesalahan atau berbuat dosa, dia akan dihukum.

300
00:20:12,961 --> 00:20:17,674
{\an8}[TEMBAKAN CEPAT]

301
00:20:19,384 --> 00:20:21,762
{\an8}[TEMBAKAN CEPAT]

302
00:20:22,554 --> 00:20:24,348
{\an8}[OLSEN] Apakah dia benar-benar ayahku?

303
00:20:26,141 --> 00:20:32,856
[PEMUTARAN MUSIK TEMA]

